about this anymore.

14:11.601 --> 14:13.353
I am really disappointed in you.

14:13.436 --> 14:14.938
I'm going to bed.

14:16.189 --> 14:18.608
We could have gone to
the seafood place!

14:18.692 --> 14:20.902
None of this would
have had happened.

14:20.986 --> 14:22.070
Really?

14:22.153 --> 14:23.613
That's your takeaway
after all this?

14:23.697 --> 14:25.282
That we should've gone
to the seafood place?

14:25.365 --> 14:26.575
Yep!

14:26.658 --> 14:28.577
Good night.

14:38.753 --> 14:40.422
- Hey.
- Hey!

14:40.505 --> 14:43.341
- Whassup?
- How's it going?

14:43.425 --> 14:45.343
It's going great.

14:45.427 --> 14:48.138
I did a few colonoscopies,

14:48.221 --> 14:49.931
ERCPS.

14:50.807 --> 14:52.392
I read a little Harry Potter.

14:52.475 --> 14:54.185
