14:54.269 --> 14:56.021
Mm. Good to know.

14:56.104 --> 14:57.939
So what's up? What's going on?

14:58.023 --> 14:59.900
Uh, I don't know.

14:59.983 --> 15:02.903
This iPad is not working.

15:02.986 --> 15:05.238
I took it to the Apple Store

15:05.322 --> 15:06.656
to see the Genius.

15:06.740 --> 15:08.074
He couldn't even figure it out.

15:08.158 --> 15:09.868
Did you really go
to the Apple Store?

15:09.951 --> 15:12.579
No, the line is too big.

15:12.662 --> 15:13.872
All right, let's see.

15:13.955 --> 15:14.956
So what's wrong with it?

15:15.040 --> 15:16.917
It is very dark.

15:17.000 --> 15:18.335
I think it's dying.

15:19.794 --> 15:21.212
Your brightness isn't up.

15:21.296 --> 15:23.089
Wonderful! You fixed it.

15:23.173 --> 15:25.425
- I'll see you later.
- Wait, wait.

15:25.508 --> 15:26.760
Sit down.

15:26.843 --> 15:27.969
What's going on?

15:28.053 --> 15:30.347
I tried to call Ma today.
She's still not answering.

15:30.430 --> 15:32.515
She's really mad at you.

15:32.599 --> 15:36.019
She's so mad at you, she
even got mad at me.

15:36.102 --> 15:38.480
I asked her to heat up a pizza.

15:38.563 --> 15:41.608
She said, "Go and
do it yourself!"

15:41.691 --> 15:43.401
I got scared.

15:44.736 --> 15:46.279
It's been two weeks.

15:46.363 --> 15:48.615
Isn't this a bit much
for just eating pork?

15:48.698 --> 15:50.325
It's not about eating pork.

15:50.408 --> 15:52.160
It's not about the religion.

15:52.243 --> 15:54.537
It's about you ignoring us,

15:54.621 --> 15:57.415
not realizing who you are.

15:57.499 --> 15:59.000
What do you mean?

15:59.084 --> 16:00.961
You see, our parents

16:01.044 --> 16:03.129
raised us to be a good Muslim.

16:03.213 --> 16:05.090
When you went out to school,

16:05.173 --> 16:06.591
we gave you a Qur'an.

16:06.675 --> 16:09.219
I don't think you ever read it.

16:09.302 --> 16:11.054
When you act like this,

16:11.137 --> 16:13.807
we feel like we failed you.

16:13.890 --> 16:16.017
You know that's not true.

16:16.101 --> 16:17.477
Look, man,

16:17.560 --> 16:19.229
you can drink.

16:19.270 --> 16:20.605
You can eat pork.

16:20.689 --> 16:22.691
You can smoke Mary Jane.

16:22.774 --> 16:25.151
That's your business.

16:25.235 --> 16:28.363
But when you do it
in front of Mom,

16:28.446 --> 16:30.573
it hurts her feelings.

16:30.657 --> 16:33.994
I get it.

16:34.077 --> 16:37.580
All right, I have to go and
watch some Super Singer.

16:37.664 --> 16:39.207
What's Super Singer?

16:39.290 --> 16:41.626
Super Singer is the Indian
version of The Voice.

16:41.710 --> 16:44.004
Only Indian people sings,

16:44.087 --> 16:45.296
no whites.

16:55.223 --> 16:59.644
"Dev, when I went to school,
my mother gave me a Qur'an,

16:59.728 --> 17:01.855
and I want to do
the same for you.

17:01.938 --> 17:04.899
If you are confused,
scared or worried,

17:04.983 --> 17:08.611
read this, and maybe you
will find some knowledge.

17:08.695 --> 17:10.905
Love, Ma."
